0", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda/", "title": "Access S3, DynamoDB with Lambda", "content_html": "S3 \uac1d\uccb4 \uc0dd\uc131 \uc774\ubca4\ud2b8\ub85c Lambda\ub97c \ud2b8\ub9ac\uac70\ud574 \ud30c\uc77c\uc744 \ucc98\ub9ac\ud558\uace0 DynamoDB\uc5d0 \uc801\uc7ac, test event\ub85c \ubc18\ubcf5 \uac80\uc99d\ud55c \uc2e4\uc2b5", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/access-s3-dynamodb-with-lambda.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/failover-for-ha/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/failover-for-ha/", "title": "Failover for HA", "content_html": "Orchestrator GUI\ub85c MySQL \ub9c8\uc2a4\ud130 \uc7a5\uc560 \uc2dc \uc790\ub3d9 \ud398\uc77c\uc624\ubc84\ub97c Docker \ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub85c \uad6c\uc131\ud558\uace0 \uc778\uc704\uc801 \ub2e4\uc6b4\uc73c\ub85c \uc2b9\uaca9\u00b7\ubcf5\uad6c\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc2e4\uc2b5\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/failover-for-ha.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Database"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/s3-object-encryption/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/s3-object-encryption/", "title": "S3 object encryption", "content_html": "S3\uc758 SSE-S3\u00b7SSE-C\u00b7SSE-KMS\u00b7DSSE-KMS \ub124 \ubc29\uc2dd \ucc28\uc774\uc640 \uc5c5\ub85c\ub4dc CLI \uc635\uc158, SSE-KMS boto3 up/download \ucf54\ub4dc\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/s3-object-encryption.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role/", "title": "VPC Endpoint with Role", "content_html": "Bastion Host\ub85c \ud504\ub77c\uc774\ube57 \uc6f9 \uc11c\ubc84\uc5d0 \uc811\uc18d\ud558\uace0 Gateway Endpoint\uc640 IAM Role\ub85c S3\u00b7DynamoDB\uc5d0 \uac8c\uc774\ud2b8\uc6e8\uc774 \uc5c6\uc774 \uc811\uadfc\ud558\ub294 \uc2e4\uc2b5", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/vpc-endpoint-with-role.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/cicd-on-single-container/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/cicd-on-single-container/", "title": "CICD on Single container", "content_html": "React \ub2e8\uc77c \ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub97c Docker\u00b7docker-compose\ub85c \uac1c\ubc1c\u00b7\uc6b4\uc601 \ud658\uacbd \ub098\ub204\uace0, Travis CI\ub85c GitHub\uc5d0\uc11c AWS Beanstalk\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc790\ub3d9 \ubc30\ud3ec\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/cicd-on-single-container.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["DevOps"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/circle-ci-basics/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/circle-ci-basics/", "title": "Circle-CI Basics", "content_html": "CircleCI orbs\ub85c \ud504\ub860\ud2b8\ub294 AWS S3\uc5d0, \ubc31\uc5d4\ub4dc\ub294 CodeDeploy\ub85c EC2\uc5d0 \uc62c\ub9ac\ub294 \ubc30\ud3ec \ud30c\uc774\ud504\ub77c\uc778\uc744 IAM \uad8c\ud55c\ubd80\ud130 \uc124\uc815\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/circle-ci-basics.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["DevOps"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/multi-container-cicd/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/multi-container-cicd/", "title": "Multi container CICD", "content_html": "React\u00b7Node\u00b7Nginx\u00b7MySQL \uba40\ud2f0\ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub97c docker-compose\ub85c \ubb36\uace0 Nginx \ub77c\uc6b0\ud305\uacfc Travis CI\ub85c AWS Beanstalk ECS\uae4c\uc9c0 \ubc30\ud3ec\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/multi-container-cicd.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["DevOps"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-proxy-layer-for-mysql/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-proxy-layer-for-mysql/", "title": "Docker Proxy Layer for MySQL", "content_html": "ProxySQL\ub85c \uc77d\uae30\u00b7\uc4f0\uae30 \ud638\uc2a4\ud2b8\uadf8\ub8f9\uc744 \ub098\ub220 \ucffc\ub9ac\ub97c \ub77c\uc6b0\ud305\ud558\uace0, Master \uc7a5\uc560 \ud6c4 14\ucd08 \ub9cc\uc5d0 \uc2b9\uaca9\ub418\ub294 \ud398\uc77c\uc624\ubc84\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc2e4\uce21\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/docker-proxy-layer-for-mysql.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Database"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-basics/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-basics/", "title": "Docker basics", "content_html": "Node \uc571\uc73c\ub85c Dockerfile\u00b7WORKDIR\u00b7\ub808\uc774\uc5b4 \uce90\uc2f1(\ube4c\ub4dc 6.7\ucd08\uc5d0\uc11c 1.8\ucd08)\u00b7\ubcfc\ub968\u00b7compose\uae4c\uc9c0 \ud6d1\uc740 \ub3c4\ucee4 \ubcf5\uc2b5 \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/docker-basics.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Docker"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-compose-and-web-gui/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-compose-and-web-gui/", "title": "Docker compose and web GUI", "content_html": "Ubuntu\uc5d0 Docker \uc124\uce58\ud558\uace0 Portainer GUI\ub85c \uad00\ub9ac, DVWA \ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108 \ub85c\ub4dc\uc640 compose\ub85c WordPress\u00b7MySQL \uc62c\ub9ac\uae30\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/docker-compose-and-web-gui.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Docker"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-volume-with-mysql/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/docker-volume-with-mysql/", "title": "Docker volume with MySQL", "content_html": "CentOS\uc5d0 percona MySQL \ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub97c \uc62c\ub9ac\uace0 \ubcfc\ub968 \ub9e4\ud551\uc73c\ub85c \ucee8\ud14c\uc774\ub108\ub97c \uc9c0\uc6cc\ub3c4 \ub370\uc774\ud130\uac00 \ub0a8\ub294 stateful \uc0c1\ud0dc\ub97c \uad6c\ud604\ud55c \uae30\ub85d", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/docker-volume-with-mysql.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["Docker"]}, 