in-vpc/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/elasticsearch-domain-in-vpc/", "title": "ElasticSearch domain in VPC", "content_html": "VPC \ud504\ub77c\uc774\ube57 \uc11c\ube0c\ub137\uc758 ElasticSearch \ub3c4\uba54\uc778\uc744 Nginx \ud504\ub85d\uc2dc\ub85c \ub9ac\ub2e4\uc774\ub809\uc158, Cognito \uc778\uc99d \uc720\ubb34\ubcc4 \uc124\uc815 \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/elasticsearch-domain-in-vpc.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["SRE"]}, {"id": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/elasticsearch-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "url": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2021/04/17/elasticsearch-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/", "title": "ElasticSearch \uc815\ub9ac", "content_html": "\uc5d8\ub77c\uc2a4\ud2f1\uc11c\uce58 \ub3c4\ud050\uba3c\ud2b8 CRUD\ubd80\ud130 \ub9e4\ud551\u00b7\uc560\ub110\ub77c\uc774\uc800\u00b7\uc778\ub371\uc2a4 \ud15c\ud50c\ub9bf\u00b7\ub864\uc624\ubc84\u00b7\ub178\ub4dc role\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc2e4\uc2b5 \uba85\ub839\uc5b4\ub85c \uc815\ub9ac", "image": "https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2021/04/17/elasticsearch-\uc815\ub9ac.png", "date_modified": "2026-07-21T21:24:03+00:00", "date_published": "2023-10-15T23:23:50+00:00", "authors": [{"name": "Jeongwon Lee"}], "tags": ["SRE"]}]}